             * @saved_func: used as a backup of the function that this ops
             *              is registered at the first time,@func will be
             *              reset to @saved_func when unregister this ops
             * @local_hash: ops hash used to speed up find ftrace ops,and
             *              for ip filter
             * @func_hash:  pointer points to ops hash,used to set filter
             *              for this ops
             * @old_hash:   the old hash
             * @trampoline: trampoline code position of this ops
             * @trampoline_size:
